----------------------------------------------------

A simple command line argment parser 

----------------------------------------------------
-----------[ BASICS OF THE ARGPARSER]---------------

argument types:
    - int         * Integer
    - float       * Float
    - double      * Double
    - string      * String
    - char        * Character
    - bool        * True or false, yes or no
    - none        * No type


================= API ::::::

################# Argparser class

argparser(int argc, char** argv)

void add_option(const char* a_name, const char* alt_name, bool *is_parsed, 
                const char* desc)

void add_option(const char* a_name, const char* alt_name, bool *is_parsed, 
                arg_type type, type* ref, const char* desc)

int parse()

void show_help(const char* message)

